{"title_page": "Higher Institute of Technology of Ivory Coast", "text_new": "{{Infobox university\n| name              = Higher Institute of Technology of Ivory Coast\n| native_name       = ''Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire (IST-CI)''\n| image_name        = \n| image_size        = \n| image_alt         = \n| caption           = \n| latin_name        = \n| motto             = ''La passion pour l'excellence''\n| mottoeng          = The passion for excellence\n| established       = 2007\n| closed            = \n| type              = Private academic institution\n| affiliation       = \n| endowment         = \n| budget            = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| chairman          = \n| chancellor        = \n| president         =Kouakou N'Guessan Fran\u00e7ois\n| vice-president    = \n| superintendent    = \n| provost           = \n| vice_chancellor   = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| dean              = \n| director          = \n| head_label        = \n| head              = \n| academic_staff    = \n| administrative_staff  = \n| students          = \n| undergrad         = \n| postgrad          = \n| doctoral          = \n| other             = \n| city              = [[Abidjan]]\n| state             = \n| province          = \n| country           =[[C\u00f4te d'Ivoire]]\n| coor              = \n| campus            = 3\n| former_names      = \n| free_label        = \n| free              = \n| colors            = \n| colours           = \n| athletics         = \n| sports            = \n| nickname          = \n| mascot            = \n| affiliations      = [[RUSTA|R\u00e9seau des Universit\u00e9s des Sciences et Technologies des pays d'Afrique au sud du Sahara]] (RUSTA)\n| website           = [http://www.rusta-istci.org/ www.rusta-istci.org]\n| logo              = \n| footnotes         = \n}}\n\nThe '''Higher Institute of Technology of Ivory Coast''' ({{lang-fr|Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire (IST-CI)}}) is a [[private university|private institution]] of higher education and research<ref>http://www.mesrsci.com/images/stories/fichierPDF/universites%20et%20post%20bts%20fevrier%202010.pdf</ref> whose headquarters is in the district of Plateau in [[Abidjan]], the economic capital of [[Ivory Coast]].\n\n==History==\n\nCreated by a group of [[Education in France|teachers-researchers]], the Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire is a [[university]] institution for scientific, cultural and professional character, enjoying corporate personality, pedagogical and scientific, administrative and financial autonomy.\n\nIt contributes to the missions of [[higher education]] and [[Scientific method|scientific research]] through five specialized [[Higher education|higher schools]].\n\nThe IST-CI is a member institution of the [[RUSTA|Network of Universities of Science and Technology of the Countries of Africa south of the Sahara]] ({{lang-fr|R\u00e9seau des Universit\u00e9s des Sciences et Technologies des pays d'Afrique au Sud du Sahara (RUSTA)}}).<ref>http://www.rusta-comrefas.org/usttg-et-istci.html</ref>\n\n==Organization==\nThe IST-CI has five specialized higher schools<ref>http://rusta-istci.org/index.html</ref> and one research centre:\n\n===Specialized higher schools===\n* Higher School of Management and Business Administration (ESMAE)\n* Higher School of Communication (ESCOM)\n* Higher School of Public Works, Mines and Geology (ESTPMG)\n* Higher School of Industrial Technology (ESTI)\n* Higher School of Applied Informatics (ESIA)\n\n===Research centre===\n* [[COMREFAS|Consortium for the Management of Basic and Applied Research in Africa south of the Sahara]] ({{lang-fr|[http://www.comrefas.com/ Consortium pour le Management de la Recherche Fondamentale et Appliqu\u00e9e en Afrique au sud du Sahara] (COMREFAS)}})\n\n==International relations==\nSince its inception, the IST-CI has worked to develop a network of international cooperation with foreign universities, including with the [[University of Poitiers]].<ref>https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:azHkDAdhDgUJ:www.univ-poitiers.fr/servlet/com.univ.collaboratif.utils.LectureFichiergw%3FCODE_FICHIER%3D1287746883994%26ID_FICHE%3D75081+higher+business+school+of+management+poitiers&hl=en&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShvNA7DpPIM9KZvQgQ6V2wQe6nUtJx1bi1ZLnRrWJzuEmem0CMg3nJf2ORKQrmTPPSDBU04_QX3gRO8Cqz_mFAGWRrrRJIbRTPk8z2U_bI40YlkpGDN17xAQtyg7RffPxt4JDUc&sig=AHIEtbSZ8TxAywNDgiZ4OCc-71Ks2tQQPg</ref>\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.rusta-istci.org/ Official website] {{in lang|fr}}\n\n==References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Universities in Ivory Coast}}\n\n{{coord|5.3264|N|4.0219|W|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Universities in Ivory Coast]]\n[[Category:Organizations based in Abidjan]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2007]]\n[[Category:2007 establishments in Ivory Coast]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Abidjan]]\n\n\n{{IvoryCoast-university-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox university\n| name              = Higher Institute of Technology of Ivory Coast\n| native_name       = ''Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire (IST-CI)''\n| image_name        = \n| image_size        = \n| image_alt         = \n| caption           = \n| latin_name        = \n| motto             = ''La passion pour l'excellence''\n| mottoeng          = The passion for excellence\n| established       = 2007\n| closed            = \n| type              = Private academic institution\n| affiliation       = \n| endowment         = \n| budget            = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| chairman          = \n| chancellor        = \n| president         =Kouakou N'Guessan Fran\u00e7ois\n| vice-president    = \n| superintendent    = \n| provost           = \n| vice_chancellor   = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| dean              = \n| director          = \n| head_label        = \n| head              = \n| academic_staff    = \n| administrative_staff  = \n| students          = \n| undergrad         = \n| postgrad          = \n| doctoral          = \n| other             = \n| city              = [[Abidjan]]\n| state             = \n| province          = \n| country           =[[C\u00f4te d'Ivoire]]\n| coor              = \n| campus            = 3\n| former_names      = \n| free_label        = \n| free              = \n| colors            = \n| colours           = \n| athletics         = \n| sports            = \n| nickname          = \n| mascot            = \n| affiliations      = [[RUSTA|R\u00e9seau des Universit\u00e9s des Sciences et Technologies des pays d'Afrique au sud du Sahara]] (RUSTA)\n| website           = [http://www.rusta-istci.org/ www.rusta-istci.org]\n| logo              = \n| footnotes         = \n}}\n\nThe '''Higher Institute of Technology of Ivory Coast''' ({{lang-fr|Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire (IST-CI)}}) is a [[private university|private institution]] of higher education and research<ref>http://www.mesrsci.com/images/stories/fichierPDF/universites%20et%20post%20bts%20fevrier%202010.pdf</ref> whose headquarters is in the district of Plateau in [[Abidjan]], the economic capital of [[Ivory Coast]].\n\n==History==\n\nCreated by a group of [[Education in France|teachers-researchers]], the Institut Sup\u00e9rieur de Technologie de C\u00f4te d'Ivoire is a [[university]] institution for scientific, cultural and professional character, enjoying corporate personality, pedagogical and scientific, administrative and financial autonomy.\n\nIt contributes to the missions of [[higher education]] and [[Scientific method|scientific research]] through five specialized [[Higher education|higher schools]].\n\nThe IST-CI is a member institution of the [[RUSTA|Network of Universities of Science and Technology of the Countries of Africa south of the Sahara]] ({{lang-fr|R\u00e9seau des Universit\u00e9s des Sciences et Technologies des pays d'Afrique au Sud du Sahara (RUSTA)}}).<ref>http://www.rusta-comrefas.org/usttg-et-istci.html</ref>\n\n==Organization==\nThe IST-CI has five specialized higher schools<ref>http://rusta-istci.org/index.html</ref> and one research centre:\n\n===Specialized higher schools===\n* Higher School of Management and Business Administration (ESMAE)\n* Higher School of Communication (ESCOM)\n* Higher School of Public Works, Mines and Geology (ESTPMG)\n* Higher School of Industrial Technology (ESTI)\n* Higher School of Applied Informatics (ESIA)\n\n===Research centre===\n* [[COMREFAS|Consortium for the Management of Basic and Applied Research in Africa south of the Sahara]] ({{lang-fr|[http://www.comrefas.com/ Consortium pour le Management de la Recherche Fondamentale et Appliqu\u00e9e en Afrique au sud du Sahara] (COMREFAS)}})\n\n==International relations==\nSince its inception, the IST-CI has worked to develop a network of international cooperation with foreign universities, including with the [[University of Poitiers]].<ref>https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:azHkDAdhDgUJ:www.univ-poitiers.fr/servlet/com.univ.collaboratif.utils.LectureFichiergw%3FCODE_FICHIER%3D1287746883994%26ID_FICHE%3D75081+higher+business+school+of+management+poitiers&hl=en&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEEShvNA7DpPIM9KZvQgQ6V2wQe6nUtJx1bi1ZLnRrWJzuEmem0CMg3nJf2ORKQrmTPPSDBU04_QX3gRO8Cqz_mFAGWRrrRJIbRTPk8z2U_bI40YlkpGDN17xAQtyg7RffPxt4JDUc&sig=AHIEtbSZ8TxAywNDgiZ4OCc-71Ks2tQQPg</ref>\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.rusta-istci.org/ Official website] {{in lang|fr}}\n\n==References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Universities in Ivory Coast}}\n\n{{coord|5.3264|N|4.0219|W|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Universities in Ivory Coast]]\n[[Category:Organizations based in Abidjan]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2007]]\n[[Category:2007 establishments in Ivory Coast]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Abidjan]]\n\n{{IvoryCoast-university-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", 